Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:08.94,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光啊 以路米艾里斯加护之名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:14.81,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才没哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:17.98,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你眼眶有点湿润
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.72,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我身上到处都很疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用这么生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:24.38,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道我们活着重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:25.67,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我很想你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.72,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不...不对 我才不想你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:36.62,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一想到不用再看到你们的脸了 我胸口就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.73,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸口就怎么了 疼得快裂开了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.98,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不...不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.85,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸口就？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.92,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸...胸口就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.73,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸口...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:49.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.74,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸口就？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.99,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吵死了平胸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:58.08,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别叫我平胸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.64,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就叫 叫个几百回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平胸平胸平胸平胸.....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:04.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.13,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}闭上嘴好好呆着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还是说你不想治好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不...不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.47,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.48,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 好像没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.68,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会欧鲁达那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.84,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:28.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.32,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:33.63,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要放松的话 等回到欧鲁达那再放松
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:44.49,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德说“你是队长” 我思考着他这句话的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为在我心里 说到队长的话就算马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.18,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要变得像马纳多那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:56.38,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种心情 确实也是有一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.08,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.12,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.06,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:12.48,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}马纳多说过 谁都有擅长和不擅长的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:16.07,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}马纳多不擅长什么 我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:22.08,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有许多不擅长的事和不足的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.99,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同伴们会帮我弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:31.26,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说不定这样就算维持了队伍的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:36.17,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我说一点都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:38.37,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己有没有尽到队长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:46.24,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过 队伍能顺畅运转 是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.97,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我和蓝德也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}战斗的时候能配合好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:55.11,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为这才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.12,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:03.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我暂时用不了魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最多只能勉强用一次治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.48,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}需要找地方冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:12.42,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不太懂魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.42,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过席赫露看起来也快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.64,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总之先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:21.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心不要刺激到小地精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:58.38,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.02,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}马利克·艾姆·帕尔克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.11,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.54,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.94,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Dead Spot受伤越多就越强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.78,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还...还要变强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.98,0:11:28.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该...该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:29.39,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是能逃得掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.81,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有这一条路 肯定逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:38.30,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一个人 最起码要留下一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:44.28,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在思考之前 身体就动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.01,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蜘蛛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.97,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.19,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.98,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.49,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在干什么 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.49,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:26.01,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.92,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.79,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没错 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.52,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:42.19,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃 听不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:49.49,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别死啊 笨蛋哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:57.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:04.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这种情况下让我不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:07.08,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是魔鬼吗 混蛋蓝德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.48,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.74,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然顽强的你这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:18.77,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我肯定不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.93,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.52,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}记得来驱散我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那样的话应该能再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.17,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:38.78,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.12,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}关乎性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.62,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是关乎性命的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.57,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.62,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:13:59.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.57,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到死都要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:09.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.08,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:22.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}动得很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别去想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.16,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.55,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.25,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天国...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欢迎回来 哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.29,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:21.71,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛 给
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.57,0:16:23.83,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.40,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Dead Spot呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.08,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.35,0:16:35.43,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.89,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好烫好烫好烫...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.02,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}醒了没
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:44.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是赏金30金
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:51.16,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等哈尔希洛醒了 大家再一起商量怎么分 蓝德说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:54.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他说因为哈尔希洛是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.49,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蓝德说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么 你有什么意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:02.35,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们去接哈尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.77,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.17,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是那个接啊 对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.92,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你跟Date Spet倒在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:12.19,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Date... Dead Spot？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:20.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正好我的剑断了 这个挺趁手的就拿过来用用看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.56,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说这个趁手...莫古索真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.15,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 啊 没有啦 这样直接用当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.84,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想送去锻冶店里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.71,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来赏金的用途已经定好一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:34.80,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等完成了 要起个可爱的名字才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.01,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.72,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}菜刀一号之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:45.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可...可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.39,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.34,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:11.24,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个 我帮你修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:24.03,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体熟悉的些微重量与感触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:28.17,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可思议地让人心情平静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:32.67,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突然让我有了实感
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:36.67,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回来了 梅丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.10,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在才说？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.70,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我听说了我听说了 小哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:01.79,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然干掉了Deat Spot 真是太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有掉小嫉妒 才没这回事呢尼日利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:09.96,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}澳大利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.65,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.90,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好了 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.31,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莲崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:28.76,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}莲崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.57,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}马纳多死后的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.28,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:41.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 莲崎不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.64,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:48.04,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是没能接受马纳多死了的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.32,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:53.50,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 谢谢你莲崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.00,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.88,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位 今天我们请客
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:05.18,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尽情喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:37.48,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.61,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:41.95,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.47,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:52.64,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个 我有事想问马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:54.28,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:57.28,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你当队长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:21:00.14,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会不会有时候觉得很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:02.99,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛觉得难受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.42,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.27,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哈尔希洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是不是长高了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:14.75,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:23.20,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天的自己和今天的自己是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.64,0:21:27.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明天的自己又会变成什么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:37.23,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们每一天都活在当下 去见明天的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:42.62,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会再来的 马纳多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.34,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这个世界生活的越久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.04,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就有一份记忆离得越来越远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.81,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该说是我们原本所在的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.57,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从别的什么地方来的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.62,0:22:29.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有个空洞 似乎忘记了什么重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.48,0:22:35.13,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这让我很不安 很焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:37.34,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从前是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:40.91,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是现在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:47.53,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脚下踏着的石阶 吸入的空气味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:52.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这让我感觉自己现在确实就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:55.24,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:23:01.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有不想忘记的事 也有不能忘记的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:03.74,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:07.86,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:10.36,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.93,0:23:16.33,TEXT_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位 走吧
